  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.4.1">
<l>añciṟaiya maṭanārā yaḷiyattāy nīyuniṉ</l>
<l>ṉañciṟaiya cēvalumā yāvāveṉ ṟeṉakkaruḷi</l>
<l>veñciṟaippuḷ ḷuyarttāṟkeṉ viṭutūtāyc ceṉṟakkāl</l>
<l>vaṉciṟaiyi lavaṉvaikkil vaippuṇṭā leṉceyyumō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Pretty-winged youthful heron, have pity.  You too having</l>
<l>your pretty-winged male, taking pity on me, [cowing] ā ā,</l>
<l>when you go as an envoy sent by me to the one high on the hot-winged bird,</l>
<l>if you were to undergo staying put  if he put [you] in a strong cage, what would it do [to you]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
